        <div class="news_content">
            
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="game-hot">
        <h3>热门游戏</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="showgame.html"><span><img src="/Content/Img/temp/game-img.jpg"></span><p>欢乐斗地主—地主连炸爽翻天今日奖励</p></a></li>
